Package project1

Class Date

java.lang.Object
project1.Date
All Implemented Interfaces:
Comparable<Date>
public class Date extends Object implements Comparable<Date>
Date class convert from mm/dd/yyyy String to Date object to use in Member class. Date object can be compared.
Author:
Ryan S. Lee, Elliott Ng

      Specified by:
      compareTo in interface Comparable<Date>
      Parameters:
      date - the object to be compared.
      Returns:
      EARLIER if this object is earlier than comparing object, LATER if this object is later than comparing object, EQUAL if both are same.
